767
00:54:15,426 --> 00:54:18,690
Young Templeton: Put
your faith in him.

768
00:54:18,777 --> 00:54:21,693
He will not disappoint
the trusting heart.

769
00:54:21,780 --> 00:54:26,698
The answer to man's dilemma
