846
01:00:12,478 --> 01:00:16,438
Billy Graham, I mean,
president of a college.

847
01:00:16,525 --> 01:00:18,223
Amazing!

848
01:00:18,310 --> 01:00:20,312
I mean, he had
a bachelor's degree

849
01:00:20,399 --> 01:00:22,314
