854
01:00:36,241 --> 01:00:38,243
Laverne: Office of
the president.

855
01:00:38,330 --> 01:00:40,158
Can you hold, please?

856
01:00:40,245 --> 01:00:45,424
Mr. Wilson, can you field this?
